retical analysis that points to a viability of our\nhypothesis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Apr 2014 18:50:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 May 2014 20:01:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 3 Jun 2014 04:12:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-06-04"}
