volving large systems that contain\nthousands of electrons are demonstrated to highlight the efficacy of our\nmethodology. The use of our method to study clusters with arbitrary point group\nsymmetries is briefly discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Apr 2014 23:03:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Oct 2014 17:04:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 25 Nov 2014 19:01:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-08"}
